In this study, we use the modified expression of j using μ(0) (=μSC) and μ(Nspin) (=μHA) as a function of Nspin, where μ(0) and μ(Nspin) are the charge mobility in spiro-OMeTAD before and after device operation; the Nspin is the number of formed or accumulated holes accompanied with spins. Then, Eq. (1) can be deformed using μ(0) and μ(Nspin) to the following equation:2j=neμ(0)1+μ(0)μ(Nspin)cNspinE.\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
